# Privacy Policy for SnackSmart

Effective Date: 01.06.2025

SnackSmart ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.

## 1. Information We Collect

### a. Crash Reports and Analytics
We use Google Firebase Crashlytics to collect anonymous crash reports and diagnostics. This helps us improve app stability. No personal information is collected.

### b. Feedback Form
If you choose to submit feedback via our in-app form, we collect:
- Your written comment
- Optional app status at the time of feedback (e.g., timestamp)

This data is stored securely using Google Firebase Firestore and used solely to improve the app.

## 2. How We Use Your Data
We use collected data to:
- Improve app functionality and fix bugs
- Respond to feedback
- Monitor app usage patterns (aggregated, non-identifiable)

## 3. Data Sharing
We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties.

We may share aggregate, anonymous analytics with service providers like Google Firebase to help improve performance.

## 4. Your Control
- You can choose not to submit feedback.
- You may disable crash reporting via your device settings (e.g., disable Google usage diagnostics).

## 5. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy. Changes will be posted in the app and on this page.

## 6. Contact
If you have questions, email us at: contact.looplet@gmail.com
